      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it clearly shows its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few small dings, and some minor paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows visible wear and some staining, though the cabin remains functional. Mechanically, it runs well, but it may require some routine maintenance soon to keep it in top shape. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone looking for dependable transportation at a reasonable price.",
