    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that\u2019s ready for the commute? This vehicle is a solid choice for anyone who values function and reliability! While it shows some honest signs of its journey\u2014including typical cosmetic wear and a few minor quirks\u2014it remains a hardworking car with plenty of miles left to offer. It\u2019s a great opportunity to get a functional, honest ride at a fair price!",
