    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-grade vehicle that has been maintained with obsessive attention to detail. The exterior features a flawless obsidian finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, reflecting a deep, mirror-like shine with absolutely zero swirl marks or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh condition; the hand-stitched leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates with precision, backed by a comprehensive, single-owner service history performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. Garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather, this car is indistinguishable from a brand-new delivery. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this vehicle stands in a class of its own.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
